---
title: Mexican Beef & Bean Enchiladas  with Charred Corn Salsa, Guacamole & Sour Cream
description: With beans, beef, tortillas, Cheddar cheese and charred yet sweet salsa, this Mexican favourite is colourful, delicious and a heap of fun to make.
Don’t forget to dollop on the avocado to really get the fiesta going!
